*******pin Map*********8
ESP32 Pin	Connected To	  |Component	  Function
GPIO 32	    Button 1 (btn1)	  | Push Button	   Input
GPIO 33	    Button 2 (btn2)	  | Push Button	   Input
GPIO 16	    Resistor r2 → LED1|Yellow LED	  Output
GPIO 17	    Resistor r3 → LED2|	Cyan LED	  Output
GPIO 18	    Resistor r1 → LED3|	Red LED	       Output
GPIO 21	    SDA	              |OLED Display     I2C Data (SDA)
GPIO 22	    SCL	              |OLED Display	    I2C Clock (SCL)
3.3V	    VCC	              |OLED Display	    Power Supply
GND	        GND Pins	      |Buttons & LEDs  Ground Connection